lines.text: Me-ow. (Wo-ow. That sure is an inferior fish. Here's what a master can catch.)
Ffffft. Nyaaaa? (Pfffft. Do you want to see what a real fish looks like?)
Meow. Meooow? (Wow... You didn't even manage to catch a plebeian fish this time?)
Nyaaaa... (Here to give tribute to my fine fishing skills again, I presume. :3)
Meowww. (Wowww. That was all the fish you had? I have more munnie than that.)
